When you open the app .
It will ask you for a webpage link ,
give it your desired webpage , say from Amazon.com then press [Enter]
Once the curl function takes the entire template out,
it will prompt you to View or Download.

View-
Opens the ternimal and runs the entire html code inside it for us to read and inspect (Ctrl+C wont work , Nerd stuff)

Download-
Takes the entire page , ban-for-ban , with an exception of links and ads (We dont do that here), gets shrunk into a minimal html file.
Then your file manager will recognise a file being downloaded and ask for the location to download.


You can open the html with any webviewer or browser and it will work.


Good luck making a High-quality Alibaba market page lol!
Anyways , Have fun!
